{"tid":1349770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寒戰其實係咪喺香港真實上演緊?","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:29:36.000Z","uid":59518,"like":149,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"1916b771fae3904b93e46ccb09827562fe1432fc","tid":1349770,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知 奴隸聰11月就會落台<br />\n下任大熱當然係行動副處長 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧炳強</span></strong> <br />\n呢排都跟出跟入<br />\n最印象深刻就係當日奴隸聰比人叫含撚時 企係隔離眼都唔眨啤撚你死個死人樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/15/28sRYJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F15%2F28sRYJ.png&h=8e9048a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一位副處長 <strong><span style=\"color: green;\">郭蔭庶</span></strong> <br />\n就比較少出鏡 淨係同柒頭呀叻一齊出過黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3015876/org/5a657ba7f0a08266a541d807c1c038f2.jpg/IGdWSpT6gNHUMPNqyz9-shv6VFemlyT3cv_oTHL_6Ew?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3015876%2Forg%2F5a657ba7f0a08266a541d807c1c038f2.jpg%2FIGdWSpT6gNHUMPNqyz9-shv6VFemlyT3cv_oTHL_6Ew%3Fv%3Dw800&h=aaded820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁兩位副處長既職責係做咩呢?<br />\n根據警犬網站資料顯示<br />\n警務處處長由兩位副處長協助，一位主管行動，轄下有兩個總部部門：行動處和刑事及保安處；<br />\n另一位主管管理事宜，轄下分三個部門：人事及訓練處、監管處和財務、政務及策劃處。<br />\n<br />\n我地睇下維基:<br />\n甲部門（行動處，'A' Department （Operations &amp; Support））下設行動部、支援部及6個警察總區，<span style=\"color: red;\">負責警務處的日常行動性事務。</span><br />\n乙部門（刑事及保安處，'B' Department（Crime &amp; Security））負責<span style=\"color: red;\">制訂警務處在刑事及保安方面的政策，以及有關事宜的整體指揮事務。</span><br />\n<br />\n換句話說 無論近期示威警犬既行動定尋晚元朗鄉黑圍毆 都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有鄧炳強份 </span></strong>亦都係HEAD住6個警察總區<br />\n<br />\n而另一位 負責人事及訓練處、監管處和財務、政務及策劃處 <br />\n就係文官咁上下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重點</strong></span> <br />\n郭蔭庶有位孿生細佬 叫<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">郭蔭庸</span></strong> 佢係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新界北總區指揮官</span></span></strong> <br />\n而<strong>元朗警區</strong>正正就係屬於新界北總區 <br />\n<br />\n究竟依家係咪<span style=\"color: gold;\">有人聯手 專登抽空新界北警力 妄顧市民安全</span><br />\n整隻大wok比行動副處長 藉呢個機會推走佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過大家最緊要記住呀<br />\n奴隸聰仲有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔夠4個月</span></strong>就落台 <br />\n嗌佢落台係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇撚用架</span></span></strong><br />\n記者一定要搵機會 問清楚兩位副處長同當區指揮官<br />\n究竟佢地既係乜野行動 乜野部處 係咪邀功 係咪拎人命黎較飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f742ece516c786031aebc66a505870cb6c6d49","tid":1349770,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd45871cb913b12664d054aabadd3c1d0e60c704","tid":1349770,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a119fc65bceaec5d72669b2deeddf6ed172c81c","tid":1349770,"uid":247180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:17:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"07d52bf340b30a53b5deb78d7bf5cf63f5eef33d","tid":1349770,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfdcaa745963ee5d32e6c7b21d46262f5d32abf","tid":1349770,"uid":264811,"like":0,"di