/><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:31:11.000Z","msg":"聽講係隔代欽點<br />\n呢條友個格同禿鷹一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"禿鷹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過聽聞郭蔭庶警隊聲望高過二佬強<br />\n完全係寒戰劇本<br />\n唔通寒戰編劇真係燈中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024bbe02013b940379d64e22e20d782ba1a669df","tid":1349770,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:39:16.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"42e3098aa24c521b112a77b85c912f1ee3a77e03","tid":1349770,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:39:33.000Z","msg":"重組警隊!!!!"},{"pid":"15f8151a2f36151eff93960cbf57a4b964a5688a","tid":1349770,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"非常時期用非常辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0906bb9e5928a392e512a8e62e1989aa72f9b5","tid":1349770,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"人黎...花生🥜"},{"pid":"a643510690e84fcf3f493b6b1e22ab48ad225575","tid":1349770,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"呢個post 有料到"},{"pid":"0b3ce98b9f07296d1c960fe7bc0d5625eb8c2a23","tid":1349770,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">差佬奪權</span>"},{"pid":"33bec358618ee202900551fa5081f5d93b2747